.TH "nvme_init_set_features_volatile_wc" 9 "nvme_init_set_features_volatile_wc" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_set_features_volatile_wc \- Initialize passthru command for Volatile Write Cache
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_set_features_volatile_wc
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "bool sv "  ","
.BI "bool wce "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "sv" 12
Save value across power states
.IP "wce" 12
Write cache enable
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Set Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_VOLATILE_WC
